metadata.name: Hidden Sorrows
metadata.description: "Faezeh" was born in one of the old neighborhoods of Bushehr city in south of iran, far from the wars and riots that the people of her land are involved in, but although she has never seen her homeland, there is always deep sadness in her face.  It is as if he shares in the pain and sorrow of the people of his land. Faezeh's family emigrated from Afghanistan to Iran when she was not yet born.
